Package: rlowdb
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight JSON-Based Database for R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mohamed El Fodil Ihaddaden
Maintainer: Mohamed El Fodil Ihaddaden <ihaddaden.fodeil@gmail.com>
Description: rlowdb is a lightweight, file-based JSON database for R, inspired by LowDB in JavaScript. 
    It provides an intuitive interface for storing, retrieving, updating, and querying structured 
    data without requiring a full-fledged database system. Ideal for prototyping, small-scale applications, 
    and lightweight data management needs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
